headline.main: Bulls Top Golden State in Warriors' 1st Game Without Durant
headline.print_headline: Bulls Top Golden State in Warriors' 1st Game Without Durant

lead_paragraph: Spotify said on Thursday it has reached 50 million paid subscribers, growing 25 percent in less than six months and extending the Swedish music streaming service's lead over its closest rival, Apple Music.
